Lectotype of 
<taxonomicName authority="Hardw., Hardwicke Drawing" authorityName="Hardw., Hardwicke Drawing" box="[445,986,1965,1991]" class="Gastropoda" family="Ficidae" genus="Ficus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="laminosa">
